page.title: 04The Royal Visit
page.content: The{Princess of Wales}came on May 30th 1985. She arrived by helicopter at Pell Lane. She was wearing a pin- striped suit, and a sailor style hat . She got here at 11 a.m.She went so fast that you only got a glimpse of her . My cousin saw her when she came out, and they got a wave.She had her lunch at the Club. After that she visited a factory to help teenagers who are unemployed.My Dad and Uncle helped to build the new old people's home because they work for Westridge the builders.My Auntie and my Nan had lunch with Princess Diana.I have got some flowers from the dinner table.They are yellow and white.After lunch she went to the factory in Ryde.Next she set off for Sandown to open the new Fire Station. Amy,Stefanie,Lisa.
